  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41f6666ec8adc1846b1cc0f2bf100762, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 1
  lines:
  - "Ah, that\u2019s a shame, I just had my wife and daughter go through this morning."
  - "Lot of weight of my shoulders knowing their ok\u2026 "
  - "It\u2019s all that\u2019s been weighing on my mind recently, but it\u2019s been
    pushing me through work at the very least."
  - "Awfully generic of me isn\u2019t it? Haha! Feels like everyone in this town
    only cares about family at times, can\u2019t say I oppose that though."
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: Haha, well thanks for the information, have a good day at work
